#

Pumpkin Seed Pasta Salad

20 min
$8
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing and nutty pasta salad loaded with vibrant veggies and crunchy pumpkin seeds, perfect for a quick lunch or side dish.

Ingredients

  • pasta (any shape): 2 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • bell pepper: 1 medium
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/2 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh basil (optional): 1/4 cup
